The near-identical efficiency across all inverters is a critical finding: **the inverter electronics are healthy.** The performance gap between INV-03 and INV-08 is not caused by inverter degradation — it originates upstream on the DC side, meaning the solar panels, string wiring, or DC combiner boxes connected to INV-03 are the likely root cause.

